That was truly the hardest thing I’ve ever done, being away from my mom & family. 
It hasn’t been easy during this process 🥺 but God is truly a way maker & miracle worker,

Happy 6 months of marriage♥️ @tonystephenss 😘

3 things we have learned together as a Godly couple: 

1. Marriage takes three to be complete. You, your partner & God🙌
2. PAY attention & LISTEN to your spouse. Don’t assume you know what they mean or feel.
3. Satan likes to exaggerate your spouses flaws & mistakes, to get you to focus on reasons why you should be upset. 

#Growth #Unity #Godisamazing

My only wish is I wish everyone can experience this amazing feeling like the one we have with each other! The love, the respect 🫡 the vulnerability and the admiration! As I am overwhelmed of gratitude and to be honest with you lost for words in awe for how God brought us together from two completely different worlds and two different states! God is truly amazing! 🥲 

I have always wanted to be the type of man that is not only successful in one area of his life but also successful in all areas as a Future Husband one day, Spiritually shepherding my family to Christ, Financially giving my family the best monetarily and Mentally overcoming any kind of challenges that come our way! Where in a world where there are so many narratives through the media that portray that a love like this doesn’t exist! I am here to say proudly and stand on top of the highest mountain 🏔️ “This type of love absolutely exists.” Just be yourself!

You have challenged me and loved me 🥰 not only on the Good days but also on the Bad! I thank God for you everyday! Happy 2 Year Anniversary Sweetheart! ♥️ I love you so so much baby and I can’t wait for what the future holds for us! 🛩️♥️♥️♥️

Started 2024 in consecration 
with the Lord🥹
Fasting & praying. Humbling my heart before Him. Nourishing my spirit. Getting baptized🤍

The spiritual war is real. The time to turn away from sin is NOW!
Back in November I was delivered from demons/spirits. 
It’s so so real guys.

”For we wrestle not against flesh and blood, but against principalities, against powers, against the rulers of the darkness of this world, against spiritual wickedness in high places.“
‭‭Ephesians‬ ‭6‬:‭12‬ ‭

First picture 2024. Second pic taken in 2019.
BIG DIFFERENCE 
I cannot say it enough how GOD TRULY CHANGED ME. 
Look at my eyes and mouth in the second pic, it’s so sexual. 
I used to always pose this way and dress very sexy seeking likes, views and attention from men. I was lost.
As I started growing my relationship with Jesus he showed me I was carrying a demon. 
The spirit of Jezebel was in me. (YouTube it)
Ladies I know the world tells us it’s okay to be sexy and show our bodies but it is not. 
It’s disrespectful to God. 
This is the devils agenda. Little girls being raised by social media and a demonic culture.
We need more women of God to stand up for our future generations. 
.
GOD IS REAL🤍

”Therefore, if anyone is in Christ, he is a new creation; old things have passed away; behold, all things have become new.“
‭‭II Corinthians‬ ‭5‬:‭17‬ ‭
